entries.npc_10: Mostly it just means people trying to kill me.  I don't think I like infamous very much.
entries.player_9: Well, that's better than being famous.
entries.npc_5: Famous?  I don't see how I could be famous.  Infamous maybe.
entries.npc_8: There was a lot more to it than just me.  Lots of my friends died that day.
entries.player_7: I hear you took out the Death Star personally.
entries.npc_4: What did they tell you?  That I'm a hero?  It's been a little overblown, but yeah, I was there at the Battle of Yavin.
entries.player_5: I have some friends in the Alliance...
entries.player_4: You've confused me with someone else.
entries.npc_6: I'm sure I'll remember it sooner or later.  Stick around and I'll let you know.
entries.player_3: Maybe, but I don't think we've met before.
entries.npc_2: Are you sure?  You seem awfully familiar.
entries.player_1: Me?  No, I'm not from around here.
entries.npc_1: There's something familiar about your face...
